        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 25–33. Male pygophore of Podisus ventralis (25–27), Podisus graziae sp. n. (28–30), and Podisus thomasi sp. n. (31–33) in dorsal (25, 28, 31), posterior (26, 29, 32) and ventral (27, 30, 33) views. Abbreviations: dp, dorsal projection; dr, dorsal rim; pa, posterolateral angle; il, inferior layer of ventral rim; par, paramere; pc, pseudoclasper; sl, superior layer of ventral rim; vp, ventral projection; vr, ventral rim. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4692475/files/figure.png" .

